<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n14230d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n14" href="#n14230d">N14 (VI.B.7)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n14all.htm#n14230d"> 230(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Halfdan / hinn / Mildi / (Bad entertainer)</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[<cite>Ynglinga Saga</cite>, cap.411:]</font> Halfdan &ldquo;had been long on Viking expeditions &hellip; He died on a bed of sickness and was buried at Borre.&rdquo; He was called <mark>Halfdan hinn Mildi oc hinn Malar illi (the bad entertainer)</mark>. <small> Charles Haliday, <a name="SKD1" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#SKD1"><cite title="source">The Scandinavian Kingdom of Dublin</cite></a>, 2nd ed. (1884) 116n</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
